casebody.data:
Tuesday, November 22, 1994

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-1739. Ridgeview Ctr., Inc. v. Lorain Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 92-D-1308. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by this court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective November 21, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
